author: The Associated Press
title: Divided House Republicans call on Paul Ryan to fill leadership vacuum
text: Divided House Republicans call on Paul Ryan to fill leadership vacuum Paul Ryan, Trey Gowdy Rep. Paul Ryan (center) arrives for a House GOP meeting Friday, Oct. 9, 2015, on Capitol Hill in the nation's capital. The pressure is on Ryan to run for House speaker in the chaotic aftermath of Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy's sudden decision to abandon his campaign for the post. (Doug Mills/ The New York Times via AP) (The Associated Press)
